<a href="https://www.apple.com.cn/newsroom/2020/11/apple-announces-app-store-small-business-program/">https://www.apple.com.cn/newsroom/2020/11/apple-announces-app-store-small-business-program/</a><br>
苹果在 11 月 18 日的一则通告，对于独立开发者是一个好消息。</p>
